  "texts": [
    "Then, the processed dataset is divided into 70% for training, 15% for testing, and 15% for validation.",
    "The training and validation sets are used for hyperparameter optimization of Incep-tionV3, while the testing set is used to evaluate the performance of the overall proposed intelligent waste classification model.",
    "Finally, in the classification phase, a multi-objective variant of beluga whale optimization (MBWO) is proposed.",
    "The proposed MBWO-based hyperparameter tuning algorithm is applied to find the best hyperparameter settings for the InceptionV3 deep learning architecture.",
    "Then, the optimized InceptionV3 is utilized to classify each test image of the adopted TrashNet dataset."
  ],
